FREE: Week Nine Football Games to Watch Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
Iowa Preps has put together a list of the games to watch this weekend on the football field. See which contests will be ones to keep a close eye as clubs are fighting it out on the gridiron now! 
Top 10 Games to Watch 
1.) South Tama at Aplington-Parkersburg2.) Regina, Iowa City at Pella Christian 3.) Dallas Center-Grimes at Glenwood 4.) Garner-Hayfield-Ventura at Clear Lake 5.) Colo-Nesco at H-L-V, Victor 6.) Iowa City, City High at Muscatine 7.) Pekin at Winfield-Mt. Union 8.) West Hancock at Bishop Garrigan9.) Exira/Elk Horn-Kimballton at Kingsley-PiersonT10.) Mediapolis at Mid-PrairieT10.)
